title: [Courtyard, Pond]
description: A waterfall cascades down into a small pond, creating ripples on the water's surface.  One of the groundskeepers stands nearby with a bucket of fish food in his hands.

A waterfall cascades down into a small pond, creating ripples on the water's surface.  A cat gingerly sticks its paw into the water, evidently trying to make a meal of one of the large fish swimming around.
